Warp Core Control Room
@w2 T minus 5:02:13
@w2 Commander Lamarr [L]
@w2 Commander Mercer [M]
@p9 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> Hello, Commander Lamarr!
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Oh, hello Commander Mercer. @w2 Nice to have you here. @w2  I've heard you are now responsible for the warp engines and the protocols. @w2 And for having overwritten my repair protocols and tests the moment you stepped on board the TITAN? @w2 So, how can I help you?
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> I am just having a look at the warp core. @w2 Impressive!
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Yes. @w2 Unbelievable what the techs have pulled out of that pile of junk in Antarctica four decades ago. 
@p9 <color=#ffffff>[L] </color>Nothing but destroyed devices and incomplete blueprints but now, somehow it just magically works. @w2 You know what I mean.
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> Yes, indeed.
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Just a question, if you don't mind? @w2 What exactly are you doing here?
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> As I said, having a look at the warp core and its optimizations.
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Hmm. @w2 Ok. @w2 Then enjoy your stay. @w2 I am setting up the final routines. @w2 Or do you want to rewrite them right away?
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> No worries. @w2 It seems there have been no issues with the schedule being moved forward, yes?@p9 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Er, @w2 ahem, @w2 No. @w2 Sure. @w2 The teams have made exceptional progress since some office-sitter decided to throw them out of their beds. @w2 This, after already working weeks with nearly no sleep.
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> That's obviously the risk of working in the expedition fleet, right?
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Ha ha. @w2 Tell you what, this whole 'expedition' thing is going a strange route. @w2 Not to mention, there's a Council that governs all the decisions and the UCH is somehow in the dark. @w2 Don't you think this requires some additional ... @w2 explanation?
@p9 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> No. What should we explain? @w2 To whom? @w2 There is nothing secret about the expedition, for those that are involved. @w2 We'll tell the people what they need to know.
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Yes. That's exactly my point! As you might know, my grandpa was the lead engineer on the Hyperion. @w2 He was not lost with the ship only for one simple reason: someone decided to reschedule his shift. @w2 I'm thankful for that, but my grandpa never managed to get rid of the stigma of 'the coward that was left behind'.
@p9 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> My dad moved to Mars with me after my grandpa's sudden death. @w2 I signed up for the fleet right after college, to show what our family is capable of. @w2 My dad said that Grandpa became crazy about this shit. @w2 Pretending the officials just want to silence everyone. @w2 Especially him personally, and the Hyperion Bereaved organization. @w2 All his stories of a 'planned accident.' @w2 The ship 'not being destroyed' and some 'threat' we are facing - all very dramatic.
@p9 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> And, to be honest, until the last 24h, I always thought this old poor man simply could not cope with what happened. @w2 When you showed up on board the Titan, I suddenly remembered one of my grandpa's stories, about some 'black suits' visiting the Hyperion a few days ahead of the mission.
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> Commander. Please...
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> I tell you what: 
@p9 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> I've been working for this project for nearly eight years now, and in these last few months, I've looked at this project and I've done the math. @w2 In the last week, and in the last 24 h in particular, so many strange things have happened.@w2 The GRAND and the TITAN each have several squads of marines on board. I checked the manifests yesterday. @w2 We have stashed away tons and tons and tons of high caliber ammo. @w2 I am an engineer. I know what these formulas and materials are made for. @w2 This is not for asteroid defense. @w2  And now you are coming on board. @w2 And the first thing you do, is to mess around with the protocols I have been developing for the last five years.
@p9 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> The adjustments we've made are coming directly from Apollon labs. @w2 Dr Greyson and Dr. Dawson?
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> I know them. @w2 But I have also looked at the changes you made. @w2 These are risky. I am not sure what they should do exactly. @w2 They don't seem to have any function that improves the efficiency of the warp drives.
@w2 <color=#9c9c9c>[M]</color> Rest assured, these have been approved by top specialists, everything is fine.
@w2 <color=#ffffff>[L]</color> Rest assured, if something goes wrong .. @w2and someone is harmed .. @w2 and I discover that it was because of your changes .. @w2 nothing will be fine .. @w2 for you.

